# Slide Reports Project Rules

## Deployment & Web Server

- This application uses **Apache** as the web server
- After making changes to the web application, restart Apache with: `service apache2 restart`
- The site is hosted at: **https://reports.slide.recipes**
- Use a browser to verify changes after deployment

## Testing

- Test API key for development/testing: `tk_4xgc378i7hfe_Ww1yeInkVpxy0Y2JBlClo6IvJjCLpQzL`
- Use this key when testing API endpoints or authentication features

## Coding Standards

- Do not use ternary operators in code
- Shell scripts should be written to be idempotent (can be run multiple times safely)

